      • buildNotLoggedInLayout

        public static com.vaadin.ui.Layout buildNotLoggedInLayout()
        Builds and returns a Layout displaying a "please log in" message. Portlets using this method must include the mail9.png and lock12.png image resources (both sized 64x64 pixels) from the src/main/resources/img folder in this project to the corresponding folder in the portlet project (usually src/main/webapp/VAADIN/themes/mytheme).
        Returns:
        a Layout informing users to log in.
